title: Grateful Dead Live at Red Rocks Amphitheatre on 1982-07-28
description:
Set 1

Shakedown Street, Beat It On Down The Line-> Greatest Story Ever Told, They Love Each Other, Mama Tried-> Mexicali Blues, Big Railroad Blues, Lazy Lightning-> Supplication-> Deal

Set 2

Women Are Smarter, Althea, Let It Grow-> He's Gone-> Truckin'-> Drums-> Spanish Jam-> Not Fade Away-> Black Peter-> Sugar Magnolia, E: It's All Over Now Baby Blue

reviews.review_text:
Lovely version of the first set... Played with Zest! Really...
The band seems to be listening.
My fondness for the second set remains, but this version of a first set pleases! As mentioned in many places, recorded in pouring rain. It is zesty!
